title: Suzy Spoon's Vegetarian Butcher
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Fast food, Take-out, Australian
description: Re-located here late-July 2013 from Enmore. Shop and kitchen making all vegan sandwiches and burgers to-order. Sells a range of vegan food products including different types of sausages made in-house; also has vegan cheese, liquid smoke, jerquee, vegg, satay sauce, tofu, tempeh, and foods. The only non-vegan item is dairy milk for coffee and tea.
